  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this study is to prospectively investigate the diagnostic performance and
      potential radiation dose reduction in coronary artery calcium scoring using the new tin
      filter system of the 3rd generation DSCT scanner.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
